    "note": "So the cabinet stood, and stands: Monday, the Crimson (Mars); Tuesday, the Amber (Sun); Wednesday, the Ochre (Jupiter); Thursday, the Verdigris (Venus); Friday, the Ultramarine (Moon); Saturday, the Bone (Mercury); Sunday, the Lead-white (Saturn). And Saturday's drawer held the Bone — quicksilver, Mercury's metal. The cabinet keeps its own order; the almanac may see to its own."
